Using $\theta = 0$ for $w = 1$:
$$
 \omega_k = \cos\frac{2\pi k}{6} + i\sin\frac{2\pi k}{6} = \cos\frac{\pi k}{3} + i\sin\frac{\pi k}{3}
$$

| $k$ | Angle | Root |
| 0 | $0$ | $1$ |
| 1 | $\frac{\pi}{3}$ | $\frac{1}{2} + \frac{\sqrt{3}}{2}i$ |
| 2 | $\frac{2\pi}{3}$ | $-\frac{1}{2} + \frac{\sqrt{3}}{2}i$ |
| 3 | $\pi$ | $-1$ |
| 4 | $\frac{4\pi}{3}$ | $-\frac{1}{2} - \frac{\sqrt{3}}{2}i$ |
| 5 | $\frac{5\pi}{3}$ | $\frac{1}{2} - \frac{\sqrt{3}}{2}i$ |

